Output assets/slyph.gif

Set Shell "bash"
Set FontSize 18
Set Width 1200
Set Height 720
Set Padding 20
Set Theme "Dracula"

Hide
Type "zig build" Enter
Sleep 3s
Show

Type "zig-out/bin/slyph" Enter
Sleep 3s

Ctrl+L
Sleep 1s
Type "example.com"
Sleep 800ms
Enter
Sleep 3s

Type "jjjj"
Sleep 1500ms
Type "k"
Sleep 1s

Type "H"
Sleep 2s

Type "q"
Sleep 1s
